    "description": "<strong>Galaxy Drift</strong> 是一款高速等距视角赛车游戏，灵感来自 8 位机和 16 位机时代的经典游戏。在令人肾上腺素飙升的银河赛车中，达到天文数字级的速度，飞越行星、恒星和黑洞，挑战物理定律。从代表银河系众多文明的驾驶员中选择你的赛手。在银河漂移联赛中角逐银河冠军，或在双人分屏模式中与朋友一决高下。<br><br><strong>《Galaxy Drift》游戏特色：</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>超过 8 名拥有独特载具的驾驶员。<br></li><li> 3 个独立的联赛杯，每个联赛杯有 3 条赛道。<br></li><li>完全支持游戏手柄<br></li><li>本地多人游戏（双人分屏游戏<br></li><li>在线和本地计时赛排行榜</li></ul><br><strong>控制选项：</strong><br>《Galaxy Drift》在比赛中提供控制你载具的三种不同方式。从经典、定向和鼠标转向中进行选择，每种转向方式都会吸引不同风格的玩家。可以轻松进行尝试，因为你可以随时更改控制方法！<br><br><u>经典：</u><br>经典控制模仿了传统的等距视角赛车控制，载具根据自己的视角而非玩家的视角而转弯。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563520/extras/77986aefa5c6c18c0eb7deb7b4bd5cdc.poster.avif?t=1754149399\" width=618 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563520/extras/77986aefa5c6c18c0eb7deb7b4bd5cdc.webm?t=1754149399\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><u>定向：</u><br>定向控制根据玩家的视角将载具转向任何方向。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563520/extras/e9532646f55857a1e79fe11c2e353ec6.poster.avif?t=1754149399\" width=618 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563520/extras/e9532646f55857a1e79fe11c2e353ec6.webm?t=1754149399\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><u>鼠标转向：</u><br>鼠标转向是一种特殊的单人控制方法，只能使用鼠标来驾驶载具。载具到光标的距离决定了速度和转弯速度。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563520/extras/be3430c4c1eea72f1912e74cfba6a201.poster.avif?t=1754149399\" width=618 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563520/extras/be3430c4c1eea72f1912e74cfba6a201.webm?t=1754149399\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563520/extras/be3430c4c1eea72f1912e74cfba6a201.mp4?t=1754149399\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>赛道选择：</strong><br>在 3 个杯赛的 9 条赛道上竞速，它们各有独特的场景和音乐。掌握这些赛道，在竞争中占据优势，夺得银河漂移联赛冠军。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563520/extras/d54ad21e1761df9cb0f03ad0e7e41b3e.avif?t=1754149399\" width=618 height=154 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563520/extras/c2eceb21ad5a51603f1df522de09802f.avif?t=1754149399\" width=618 height=154 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563520/extras/258dac477f6d8f1009787a910fbecbec.avif?t=1754149399\" width=618 height=154 /></span><br><br><strong>赛手选择：</strong><br>从 8 个以上的赛手中进行选择，每个赛手都有独特的载具和不同的属性，并各自具有优势和劣势，选择你最喜欢或最适合当前赛道的赛手吧。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563520/extras/044c6b18e5fd19bed1512c097a72a64f.poster.avif?t=1754149399\" width=618 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563520/extras/044c6b18e5fd19bed1512c097a72a64f.webm?t=1754149399\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>大奖赛模式</strong><br>选择大奖赛模式，在连续的比赛中与对手一决高下。需要获得前三名才能解锁下一个杯赛。在所有杯赛中获得第一名，成为银河漂移联赛冠军。在大奖赛模式中，还可以在每条赛道上找到秘密徽章。全部找到它们才能解锁特殊奖励！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563520/extras/3632313b74b5acdeba177c2ce84496a9.avif?t=1754149399\" width=618 height=154 /></span><br><br><strong>排行榜：</strong><br>在计时赛模式中考验你的技能。将你的赛手推向极限，在每条赛道上取得最佳成绩。将你的最佳成绩保存到本地排行榜或上传到 Steam，与他人分享你的胜利。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563520/extras/ab68f0c7e52ddc60cac974c2989ae2e3.avif?t=1754149399\" width=618 height=154 /></span><br><br><strong>原声音乐：</strong><br>游戏中还包括由 H4MSTER 制作的精彩原声音乐。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563520/extras/9ac07979b00791c0d4efa40b1a13ee9f.avif?t=1754149399\" width=618 height=154 /></span>",
